    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486050/extras/35315f8d76f43e8fc55b8e76bc1c4291.webp?t=1629231743\" width=106 height=40 /></span><br>Learn the traditional Japanese game of Shogi. <br>Examine all aspects of the ancient strategy game, including the Japanese names of important game elements.<br>By the time you've finished studying, you'll be able to distinguish 詰み from 二歩 without breaking a sweat.<br>Each aspect of the game is explained separately, so you'll develop your Shogi playing style at your own pace.<br>From piece movements, to drops, promotion and strategic formations, you'll learn Shogi inside out!<br>Challenge yourself with over 60 <i>Tsume Shogi</i> puzzles and become an expert in endgame strategy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486050/extras/99a8eec7f08f6e98262e227e817affc0.webp?t=1629231743\" width=83 height=42 /></span><br>Play against a wide variety of AI opponents, at a level of your choosing.<br>As your skill grows, you can dial up the difficulty to ensure a stimulating strategic challenge.<br>In-game indicators provide helpful reminders of each piece's available movements, letting you focus on choosing the best move.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1486050/extras/dd175073f7903d48d50894019fdbb849.webp?t=1629231743\" width=139 height=36 /></span><br>Once you've learned the ropes, why not enter the Shogi leagues?<br>Choose from the Sendai, Osaka, Sapporo and Tokyo leagues. Each league has a range of AI opponents to challenge you at every level.<br>To progress through the leagues, you'll develop your technique and employ a wide range of Shogi tactics.<br>With a sound strategy, victory can be yours.<br><br>Are you ready? Let's learn Shogi!",
